REM android_notifications.duck
REM Opens the Android notification shade via Win+N.
REM Demonstrates system-level HID keyboard access.
REM Tested on Samsung One UI with physical keyboard.
REM Copy to: /sdcard/lab/ble/blueduck/scripts/

HUMAN_MODE ON
HUMAN_SPEED NORMAL

REM Open notification shade (Win+N)
GUI n
DELAY 1500
